---

<BaseLayout
  title="HubSpot Dashboards for Japan Revenue Visibility | Consilegy"
  description="Default HubSpot dashboards show global aggregate data. Japan-facing teams need separate dashboard views tracking Japan MQL volume, pipeline value, sales cycle length, win rate, and quarterly revenue."
